org.thymeleaf.processor.element.IElementProcessor, org.thymeleaf.processor.element.IElementTagProcessor, org.thymeleaf.processor.IProcessor
public class MultiLineTextTagProcessor extends AbstractAttributeRemovalAttributeTagProcessor
Attribute tag processor for multi-line text.

Escape text and convert line-break characters to <br> element. Support CR, LF, and CRLF as line-break characters.

作成者:
Atsushi Yoshikawa
